## table card | doc="Person card for the System User. Explicit id=1 mirrors user_account.id=1 so activity actor lookups and any task happen-to-be-assigned-to-System scenarios resolve. ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING short-circuits the entire CTE chain on re-apply (the activity / attribute_value CTEs SELECT FROM the card CTE, so an empty result cascades through). Dev / demo person cards live in demo.hcsv." | on_conflict="id"
