## table card | under=tpl_project | alias=tpl_sc_comms | doc="Comms screen (Gate 7 of email_comm_spec). Layout 'comms' → the CommsList body lists the project's comm cards directly (comm → task → project, project_id-scoped), each with a phase-toned comm_status badge + parent-task link; a row opens its task whose COMMS section replies / advances / closes the thread. flow_ref points at the template's comm flow; toggle_groups filter by comm_status phase (active / terminal) INDEPENDENTLY of task status — the phase toggle is attr-aware so it composes a comm_status has_phase leaf. default_create_status overrides to 'Open'." | on_conflict="id"
